@node WTF "WTF"

                           @{" What The Fuck Is This ? " link " "}

   Hi this is !LAiRFiGHT! plonking at the keyz. Just wanted to tell you that
 this is my first musicdisk released under the fLE tag, but definitely not the
 last. However, I don't think I'll use MusiclineEditor anymore, unless I get a
    faster machine. I can't think of _anything_ being more annoying than the
  bloody requester popping up all the time saying "You need more CPU power!".

  Anyway, greetings to Jogeir for making such wonderful music. I suppose I got
   a bit inspired by his works; the tune called Deep Blue is, well, very much
   sounding like some parts of the Face Another Day tunes written by Jogeir.

    Well, 'nuff said. There are a whole bunch of persons greeted in the demo
 itself, and I wouldn't take up your valuable time by repeating them here; So I
                   can't think of anything else to say than:

         - Never put off 'til tomorrow what you can avoid altogether -

                     Keep diggin' - !LAiRFiGHT! of fLATLiNE


                                                                       @{" BACK " link Index}


